pullRequest.bodyText:
Fixes #1280
This PR is ready for review.
Risk
This PR makes minor API changes.
Testing Plan

 I have verified that I have not introduced new warnings in this PR (or explain why below)
 I have run the unit tests with this PR
 I have tested this PR against Core and verified behavior (if applicable, if not applicable, explain why below).
 I have tested Android, Java SE, and Java EE

Unit Tests
Unit test were added in SubscribeButtonManagerTest
Core Tests
Tested against core using sdl_HMI
Summary
Added the ability to subscribe to hard buttons via the screen manager. Ex:
 onButtonListener = new OnButtonListener() {
            @Override
            public void onPress(ButtonName buttonName, OnButtonPress buttonPress) {
            }

            @Override
            public void onEvent(ButtonName buttonName, OnButtonEvent buttonEvent) {
            }

            @Override
            public void onError(String info) {
            }
        };
        //subscribre
        sdlManager.getScreenManager().addButtonListener(ButtonName.PRESET_1,onButtonListener);
        //unsubscribe
        sdlManager.getScreenManager().removeButtonListener(ButtonName.PRESET_1,onButtonListener);

Changelog
Enhancements

Added the ability to subscribe to hard buttons via the screen manager.

CLA

 I have signed the CLA

